Ronke Ademiluyi bụ ọkachamara n'ihe gbasara ejiji na onye ọchụnta ego na Naijiria.

A mụrụ Ademiluyi na England, United Kingdom, mana ọ bụ onye Ile-Ife na Osun State, na ndịda odida anyanwu nke Naịjịrịa Ọ bụ onye guzobere Africa Fashion Week, ọrụ na-akwalite ndị na-emepụta ejiji Africa site na ndị enyemaka ya, Africa Fashion Week Nigeria na Africa Fashion Week London.
